* // ---------- System Testing ---------- // *

- Similar to integration testing
- Complete system
    - Application and environment
- Finds defects
    - Between pieces
    - System as a whole

What happens in system testing?:
    Anything that requires the entire system to be running.

    - Performance
        - Stress tests for reliability
        - Load tests for scalability
    - Security scans
    - Usability and UX
    - Compatibility

* // ---------- Regression Testing ---------- // *

# Regression
    - Software bug
    - Feature fails after a change
    - Rerun unit and integration tests after making a change